quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  26,84,"WaЙ—anaa mi jaЕ‹ta labaaЙ—o e mantoore moЖґЖґere e Й—en gire aroyay Й—e Й“aawo am."
  26,85,"WaЙ—aa lam jeyaaЙ—o e Й“en ronooЙ“e galleeji Aljanna Й—in Й—i neemintoo e nder muuЙ—um jeyaaЙ“e MaaЙ—a gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, hoЙ—inaa lam e nder majji."
  26,86,"Yawtanaa baaba am; kanko o laatinoke jeyaaЙ—o e majjuЙ“e Й“en gaay Goonga kan sabu sirku ngun, Ibraahiima du'anii ben makko ko adii Й“anngannde mo wonndema kanko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e yimЙ“e Jahiimi Й“en. Tuma nde Й—um Й“anngannoo mo, o danndii mo o du'anaaki mo [hannde kadi]."
  26,87,"Wata A wirtiroyam Lepte Й—en Г‘alnde yimЙ“e Й“en immintinoytee fii hasboore nden."
  26,88,"Г‘alnde nde nafataa e muuЙ—um jawdi ndi neЙ—Й—o on faggitii Й—um ka aduna makko, wanaa kadi Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“e o laatinoo himo wallitora Й—um."
  26,89,"Si wanaa on arduЙ—o ka Alla e Й“ernde hisunde; hara sirku e naafiqaaku alaa e mayre, yiingo e hawtaare alaa e mayre, haray pellet, kanko o nafturay jawdi makko ndi o nafkunoo ndin ka Laawol Alla, e Й“iЙ—Й“e makko wonuЙ“e du'anaade mo Й“en kadi."
  26,90,"Aljanna on Й“annanee hulirooЙ“e Joomi mu'un Й“en Й—oftagol YamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in, e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in."
  26,91,"Ka Mofturu Yiite ngen feГ±Г±inanee majjuЙ“e Й“en, Й“en majjuЙ“e gaay Diina Goongaha kan."
  26,92,"ЖЃe wi'anee ka maЖґinngol Й“e: Honto ko wonunoЙ—on rewude kon immorde e sanamuuji Й—in?"
  26,93,"On reway Й—i gaanin Alla? Taw si Й—i walliray on haЙ—anngol on Lepte Alla Й—en, kaa kannji Й—i wallay ko'e-majji?"
  26,94,"WoЙ“Й“e e maЙ“Й“e werlee e hoore woЙ“Й“e ka Jahiima e Й“en majjinЙ“e Й“e."
  26,95,"E wallooЙ“e Ibliisa Й“en immorde e Seytanuuji Й—in fow, hay gootil e majji ittintinaaka."
  26,96,"ЖЃen sirkooЙ“e wonunooЙ“e rewde tanaa Alla, Й“e jogitii Й“e kafidaaЙ“e gaanin Alla, tawi kanЙ“e hiЙ“e wennjondirde e Й“en rewnooЙ“e Й“e gaanin Alla, Й“e wi'i:"
  26,97,"Men woondirii Alla gomЙ—ii hari men laatike e nder majjere Й“anngunde gaayi Goonga kan."
  26,98,"Tuma nde men fotindirnoo on e Joom tageefooji Й—in fow majji, men rewiri on wano men rewirta Mo non."
  26,99,"Majjinaali men gaayi Laawol Goongawol ngol si wanaa Й“en bonЙ“e nodduЙ“e faade e rewugol Й“e gaanin Alla."
  26,100,"Laatanaaki men tefooЙ“e Й“e no tefanoya men ka Alla fii yo O danndu men immorde e lepte Makko Й—en."
  26,101,"Laatanaaki men giЙ—o laaЙ“uЙ—o giggol mo no hiwa men o tefanoya men."
  26,102,"Sinndo no woodannoo men artireede ka ngurndam aduna, men wona jeyaaЙ“e e gomЙ—inЙ“e Alla Й“en."
  26,103,"Pellet, wonii e koo ko jaЕ‹taa Й—oo immorde e fillayee fii Ibraahiima (yo o his), e waЙ—tinirde fennuЙ“e Й“en tasakuyee, wonannde taskotooЙ“e Й“en, Й“urЙ“e heewude e maЙ“Й“e wonaali gomЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,104,"Anndu Joomi maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o- ko Kanko woni tedduЙ—o YoЙ“totooЙ—o ayЙ“e Makko Й“en, YurmeteeЙ—o on tuubuЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e."
  26,105,"YimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en fenni NulaaЙ“e Й“en, tuma nde Й“e fennunoo Nuuhu (yo o his)."
  26,106,"Tuma nde Saalihu musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on ka dammbe (asko) wi'annoo Й“e: Enee, on hulataa Alla, acciron rewugol tanaa Makko sabu kulol Makko?!"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi NulaaЙ—o mooЙ—on, Alla Nulii lam e mooЙ—on, ko mi hoolaaЙ—o mi Й“eydataa e dow ko Alla Wahayini kon e am, mi uytataa kadi."
  26,108,"Huliree Alla Й—oftagol YamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aani Makko Й—in, Й—oftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi haЙ—ata on kon e muuЙ—um."
  26,109,"Mi Й—aЙ“Й“iraali on njoЙ“di fii ko mi yottinanta Joomi am kon e mooЙ—on, njoЙ“di am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji Й—in wanaa e tanaa Makko."
  26,110,"Huliree Alla Й—oftagol YamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aani Makko Й—in, Й—oftee lam e ko mi yamirta on kon, e ko mi haЙ—ata on kon e muuЙ—um."
  26,111,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani mo: Enee, hara men gomЙ—inte -an Nuuhu- men jokka ko adduЙ—aa kon men gollira, hara le pellet, jokkuЙ“e ma Й“en ko e yimЙ“e jaasuЙ“e Й“en Й“e jeyaako e hoohooЙ“e e teddinaaЙ“e Й“en alaa e maЙ“Й“e?!"